1
00:01:12,920 --> 00:01:13,519
Laifu

2
00:01:15,079 --> 00:01:16,920
What are you doing in my room, Laifu?

3
00:01:21,480 --> 00:01:22,640
What are you doing?

4
00:01:22,680 --> 00:01:24,040
What did you do to me last night?

5
00:01:24,079 --> 00:01:24,599
Speak!

6
00:01:26,719 --> 00:01:27,680
Miss Bai, I must say...

7
00:01:28,239 --> 00:01:29,920
Perhaps you should look at yourself first.

8
00:01:30,079 --> 00:01:31,599
Your clothes are perfectly neat from head to toe.

9
00:01:31,719 --> 00:01:32,879
What could I possibly have done?

10
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:34,040
I...

11
00:01:36,319 --> 00:01:37,400
I should be asking you!

12
00:01:37,640 --> 00:01:38,519
You held me so tightly...

13
00:01:39,079 --> 00:01:40,120
What were you trying to do?

14
00:01:41,599 --> 00:01:42,840
I held you?

15
00:01:43,159 --> 00:01:44,879
How could I possibly have held you?

16
00:01:47,159 --> 00:01:48,840
Even if... even if I did hold you...

17
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:50,359
Don't you have your own room?

18
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:51,879
Couldn't you have walked back yourself?

19
00:01:53,280 --> 00:01:54,920
You held me so tightly...

20
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:55,959
How could I move?

21
00:01:57,120 --> 00:01:57,480
I...

22
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:59,079
I held you that tightly?

23
00:01:59,319 --> 00:01:59,799
I...

24
00:02:00,519 --> 00:02:02,959
Miss, Officer Gu is here to see Young Master Laifu.

25
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:04,280
The young master isn't in his room.

26
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:05,840
Understood.

27
00:02:08,319 --> 00:02:09,719
You had her come looking for you again?

28
00:02:10,039 --> 00:02:11,280
This time it really wasn't me.

29
00:02:12,919 --> 00:02:14,800
There was a murder here last night.

30
00:02:15,599 --> 00:02:16,639
Though it's already been closed - not by me.

31
00:02:16,800 --> 00:02:17,319
But...

32
00:02:21,159 --> 00:02:23,319
I suspect it's related to the Serpent Immortal.

33
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:24,919
Master Bai isn't here.

34
00:02:25,680 --> 00:02:27,400
So we must ask you, the new head, to help.

35
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:30,080
Wasn't it already closed?

36
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:32,719
That's the official conclusion.

37
00:02:33,599 --> 00:02:34,599
But personally, I believe...

38
00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:36,759
Someone must be...

39
00:02:37,159 --> 00:02:39,800
...using the immortal's name to commit crimes.

40
00:02:44,560 --> 00:02:45,520
Crime scene.

41
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:48,039
Unauthorized personnel, don't touch anything.

42
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:48,800
Step aside.

43
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:01,560
Let's go, this way.

44
00:03:20,879 --> 00:03:21,879
The deceased is named Gao Shan.

45
00:03:22,919 --> 00:03:24,000
When we found him...

46
00:03:24,879 --> 00:03:26,039
...he was curled up completely.

47
00:03:26,319 --> 00:03:27,159
His skin was festering...

48
00:03:28,080 --> 00:03:28,800
His entire body...

49
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:31,560
...as if hiding from something.

50
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:33,240
Where was the body found?

51
00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:41,639
Cause of death?

52
00:03:43,080 --> 00:03:43,680
Asphyxiation.

53
00:03:44,919 --> 00:03:47,639
No signs of forced entry.

54
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:49,719
