59
00:03:56,319 --> 00:03:58,520
Your police work is quite lax, isn't it?

60
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:00,039
What?

61
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:03,039
That's why I must investigate personally.

62
00:04:04,159 --> 00:04:04,800
Officer Gu...

63
00:04:06,039 --> 00:04:07,840
Did he have any family or friends?

64
00:04:08,759 --> 00:04:10,280
His wife died in childbirth.

65
00:04:11,199 --> 00:04:12,280
His only son...

66
00:04:12,879 --> 00:04:14,439
...drowned three days ago.

67
00:04:15,599 --> 00:04:17,839
After his son's death...

68
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:19,639
...strange things occurred.

69
00:04:22,079 --> 00:04:22,839
Strange things?

70
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:25,199
At Heixiazi Mountain outside town...

71
00:04:25,279 --> 00:04:26,600
...there's an abandoned mansion.

72
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:29,040
Rumored to revive the dead and cure all ills.

73
00:04:29,759 --> 00:04:32,040
Gao Shan took his child there.

74
00:04:39,399 --> 00:04:41,560
Master Wei, save my child!

75
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:42,839
Master Wei!

76
00:04:43,279 --> 00:04:44,160
Master Wei!

77
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:47,720
Please, save my child!

78
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:51,879
Master Wei!

79
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:54,240
I beg you, save my child!

80
00:04:56,079 --> 00:04:56,800
Chang'an.

81
00:04:58,319 --> 00:04:59,240
Go see.

82
00:05:02,439 --> 00:05:02,920
Yes.

83
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:11,319
The dead cannot return.

84
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:13,839
Yet this Master claims there's a way.

85
00:05:14,879 --> 00:05:16,519
Only this method...

86
00:05:33,399 --> 00:05:35,000
The dead cannot return to life.

87
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:37,399
This believer, please return.

88
00:05:37,519 --> 00:05:38,279
Master Wei

89
00:05:38,720 --> 00:05:40,040
He's my only child.

90
00:05:40,360 --> 00:05:42,240
I'll give you all my possessions.

91
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:44,439
It's not about money.

92
00:05:45,319 --> 00:05:46,680
Life and death are fated.

93
00:05:47,199 --> 00:05:48,600
To defy heaven's will...

94
00:05:49,319 --> 00:05:50,639
brings calamity.

95
00:05:50,879 --> 00:05:53,519
Please, save my child.

96
00:05:53,759 --> 00:05:54,879
Please help me.

97
00:05:55,079 --> 00:05:56,480
Save my child.

98
00:05:58,319 --> 00:05:59,839
There is a way...

99
00:06:00,680 --> 00:06:04,920
but it requires your lifespan.

100
00:06:05,439 --> 00:06:05,959
Agreeable?

101
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,120
If it saves my child,

102
00:06:07,639 --> 00:06:08,800
I'll do anything.

103
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:14,639
To save all from suffering

104
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:16,920
is my sacred duty.

105
00:06:19,560 --> 00:06:22,680
Heaven has its ways,

106
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:26,319
earth its spirits.

107
00:06:26,839 --> 00:06:30,079
Yin yang displaced,

108
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:33,120
fate overturned.

109
00:06:33,319 --> 00:06:35,920
This life for that life.

110
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:51,600
Folklore says

111
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:52,800
snakes bridge worlds.

112
00:06:53,399 --> 00:06:56,120
They say Master Wei

113
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:58,800
commands snakes to steal life.

114
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:37,040
Dawa, you're awake.

115
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:37,680
Listen.

116
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:40,720
Chant this all the way home:

117
00:07:41,439 --> 00:07:43,560
"Departed soul, swiftly return."

118
00:07:44,279 --> 00:07:44,920
Remember:

119
00:07:45,399 --> 00:07:46,439
Before reaching home,

120
00:07:46,839 --> 00:07:48,199
no matter what happens

121
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:50,040
or what you hear,

122
00:07:50,879 --> 00:07:52,120
never look back.

123
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:53,639
This is vital.

124
00:07:54,439 --> 00:07:54,920
Understood.

125
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:56,199
I know.

126
00:07:57,639 --> 00:07:59,319
"Departed soul, swiftly return."

127
