130
00:08:08,199 --> 00:08:10,480
"Departed soul, swiftly return."

131
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:12,800
"Departed soul, swiftly return."

132
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:13,639
Father...

133
00:08:14,519 --> 00:08:15,720
I'm cold.

134
00:08:19,519 --> 00:08:20,399
Can't look back.

135
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:23,160
"Departed soul, swiftly return."

136
00:08:23,439 --> 00:08:25,160
Father... "Departed soul..."

137
00:08:25,519 --> 00:08:26,680
I'm tired.

138
00:08:27,839 --> 00:08:29,519
Just rest... no looking back.

139
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:31,959
"Departed soul..." Father...

140
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:32,679
Father!

141
00:08:33,039 --> 00:08:34,159
