142
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:36,080
They're taking me!

143
00:08:36,399 --> 00:08:37,440
Father!

144
00:08:38,879 --> 00:08:39,480
Dawa!

145
00:08:40,799 --> 00:08:41,440
Dawa!

146
00:08:46,879 --> 00:08:47,480
Father!

147
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:48,480
Father!

148
00:08:49,039 --> 00:08:49,879
Father! I'm scared!

149
00:08:50,399 --> 00:08:51,960
Quick! Take me home!

150
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:52,600
Father!

151
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:56,039
Soon after returning,

152
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:58,000
Gaoshan died.

153
00:08:59,559 --> 00:09:00,799
In our Northeast,

154
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:05,399
snakes becoming immortals

155
00:09:05,799 --> 00:09:08,960
are called Serpent Immortals.

156
00:09:10,799 --> 00:09:12,159
Those who commune with them

157
00:09:12,279 --> 00:09:13,279
are Shamans.

158
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:16,279
But

159
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:18,159
we've never heard

160
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:21,120
of raising the dead.

161
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:23,519
To learn Master Wei's tricks,

162
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:25,120
let's investigate.

163
00:09:25,799 --> 00:09:26,960
I know the location.

164
00:09:27,720 --> 00:09:28,240
Wait.

165
00:09:29,919 --> 00:09:31,679
Going directly is too obvious.

166
00:09:31,960 --> 00:09:32,759
We'll be spotted.

167
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:33,840
What's our cover?

168
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:36,600
I've got it.

169
00:09:37,240 --> 00:09:39,159
Master Wei "cures all ills," right?

170
00:09:39,759 --> 00:09:41,600
Someone can fake illness.

171
00:09:42,039 --> 00:09:42,679
Fake illness?

172
00:09:43,559 --> 00:09:44,399
Who'll do it?

173
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:59,799
I serve the Serpent Immortal,

174
00:11:00,600 --> 00:11:01,840
blessed with power

175
00:11:02,840 --> 00:11:07,200
to cure all ailments

176
00:11:08,480 --> 00:11:12,039
and ease worldly pains.

177
00:11:16,360 --> 00:11:19,440
May your hearts be kind.

178
00:11:23,399 --> 00:11:24,840
Gaoshan attended this gathering.

179
00:11:25,440 --> 00:11:26,960
Master Wei's words

180
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:28,519
sound convincing.

181
00:11:29,879 --> 00:11:30,919
Don't listen to his words,

182
00:11:31,879 --> 00:11:32,840
watch his actions.

183
00:11:34,120 --> 00:11:34,600
Right.

184
00:11:51,120 --> 00:11:51,799
My leg is healed.

185
00:11:52,000 --> 00:11:54,200
Even a decade-old ailment can be cured.

186
00:11:54,519 --> 00:11:55,639
I can stand up.

187
00:11:56,879 --> 00:11:57,440
I can stand up.

188
00:11:57,559 --> 00:11:58,759
The Great Immortal has manifested!

189
00:12:01,279 --> 00:12:02,679
The Great Immortal has manifested!

