The Great Immortal has manifested!

192
00:12:07,039 --> 00:12:08,399
The Great Immortal has manifested!

193
00:12:08,919 --> 00:12:09,720
The Great Immortal has manifested!

194
00:12:09,879 --> 00:12:11,759
Bless us, Great Immortal.

195
00:12:12,720 --> 00:12:13,360
Master Wei.

196
00:12:14,159 --> 00:12:14,799
Master Wei.

197
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:19,279
Young man,

198
00:12:19,559 --> 00:12:21,200
this is your first time here, right?

199
00:12:22,559 --> 00:12:23,240
No worries.

200
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:26,080
You're now one of us.

201
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:27,080
Master Wei.

202
00:12:27,799 --> 00:12:29,919
My husband has been sickly since childhood.

203
00:12:30,399 --> 00:12:31,720
It's been so long.

204
00:12:31,919 --> 00:12:33,320
Could you please examine him?

205
00:12:33,600 --> 00:12:36,519
Master Wei can only heal one person per day.

206
00:12:36,879 --> 00:12:38,039
If you seek treatment,

207
00:12:38,440 --> 00:12:39,360
you must wait.

208
00:12:41,240 --> 00:12:42,399
How long must we wait?

209
00:12:42,559 --> 00:12:44,159
If there's a chance,

210
00:12:44,399 --> 00:12:45,399
you'll get your turn.

211
00:12:46,919 --> 00:12:49,000
No, we truly can't wait any longer.

212
00:12:58,600 --> 00:12:59,159
Let's go.

213
00:13:15,240 --> 00:13:16,320
My mother is gravely ill.

214
00:13:16,720 --> 00:13:18,960
The doctor says she won't last long.

215
00:13:19,679 --> 00:13:21,720
Please, have mercy and save my mother.

216
00:13:22,440 --> 00:13:24,679
I've brought money - all the money.

217
00:13:24,840 --> 00:13:26,240
I've said it many times,

218
00:13:26,639 --> 00:13:29,279
your case isn't about money.

219
00:13:30,120 --> 00:13:32,399
As the saying goes, life and death are fated.

220
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:35,279
If I arrange treatment for you early,

221
00:13:36,679 --> 00:13:37,840
it might affect

222
00:13:37,879 --> 00:13:39,919
other devotees' lives.

223
00:13:41,039 --> 00:13:42,000
I... I...

224
00:13:42,039 --> 00:13:44,480
You should wait in line.

225
00:13:45,720 --> 00:13:47,279
I know this is wrong,

226
00:13:48,080 --> 00:13:49,919
but I must save my mother.

227
00:13:50,519 --> 00:13:52,320
We only have each other.

228
00:13:52,559 --> 00:13:53,519
If she dies,

229
00:13:53,720 --> 00:13:55,200
I can't go on living.

230
00:13:55,720 --> 00:13:58,200
Master Wei, I beg you.

231
00:13:58,320 --> 00:13:59,639
Please save my mother.

232
00:14:00,000 --> 00:14:01,919
I beg you, Master Wei.

233
00:14:02,200 --> 00:14:03,360
I beg you.

